==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Comber
<hw>Comb"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
combs; one whose occupation it is to comb wool, flax, etc. Also, a
machine for combing wool, flax, etc.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A long, curling wave.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Comber</ent>⟦br⟧

